@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<div class="hero-section d-flex align-items-center mb-5"
     style="min-height: 40vh; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1, #A78BFA);">
    <div class="container text-white text-center">
        <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold">About Me</h1>
        <p class="lead mt-3">
            A glimpse into my background, skills, and passion for technology.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Outlined Cards Section -->
<div class="container my-5">
    <!-- row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 makes 1 column on small screens, 2 columns on medium+ -->
    <!-- g-4 adds a gap of 1.5rem between columns and rows -->
    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 g-4">

        <!-- 1. About Me -->
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border border-2 border-secondary">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title fw-bold">About Me</h2>
                    <p>
                        Hello! I’m <strong>Gabriel Vega</strong>, a dedicated
                        <strong>software developer</strong> and technology enthusiast
                        with over <strong>20 years of professional experience</strong>—much
                        of it spent at the intersection of <strong>education</strong> and
                        <strong>technology</strong>. While I’ve taught programming and math
                        in classroom settings, my true passion lies in
                        <strong>innovating</strong>, <strong>building</strong>, and
                        <strong>delivering</strong> robust software solutions.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2. My Technical Toolkit -->
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border border-2 border-secondary">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title fw-bold">My Technical Toolkit</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Programming Languages:</strong> Proficient in
                            <em>Java</em>, <em>C</em>, <em>C#</em>, <em>C++</em>, and <em>Python</em>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Web &amp; Cloud:</strong> Skilled in <em>HTML</em>,
                            <em>CSS</em>, <em>JavaScript</em>, <em>SQL / Azure SQL</em>,
                            and Docker/Kubernetes for containerization
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Frameworks &amp; Tools:</strong> Experienced with
                            <em>Visual Studio</em>, GitHub, Postman, Salesforce, and Doxygen
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Cross-Platform Dev:</strong> .NET MAUI, XAML, plus
                            <em>Linux/Windows</em> environments
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Robotics &amp; Hardware:</strong> Arduino, VEX,
                            RoboBlocky, Linkbot
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3. Bridging Education & Tech -->
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border border-2 border-secondary">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title fw-bold">Bridging Education &amp; Tech</h2>
                    <p>
                        My background in <strong>teaching</strong> not only honed my
                        communication and mentorship skills but also gave me a unique
                        viewpoint for designing software—particularly solutions that
                        improve user learning and engagement. Some highlights include:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Developing and integrating <em>C-based</em> and <em>C#</em>
                            applications for robotics programs
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Introducing <em>Docker</em> for streamlined deployments
                            and environment consistency
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Mentoring teams on <em>agile methodologies</em>,
                            test-driven development, and continuous integration
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 4. Why I’m Excited About Tech -->
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border border-2 border-secondary">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title fw-bold">Why I’m Excited About Tech</h2>
                    <p>
                        Having led interdisciplinary STEM/robotics classes, I’ve
                        witnessed firsthand how <strong>hands-on tech</strong> can
                        empower people and organizations. I’m now focusing on
                        <strong>full-time software development</strong>, eager to:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Build scalable <em>.NET</em> or <em>Java</em> applications</li>
                        <li>Explore <em>AI</em> and data-driven projects</li>
                        <li>Contribute to platforms that reshape how people interact with technology</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 5. Beyond the Code -->
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border border-2 border-secondary">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title fw-bold">Beyond the Code</h2>
                    <p>
                        When I’m not coding or prototyping, you might find me:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Experimenting with new <em>IoT</em> or robotics projects</li>
                        <li>Reading up on the latest <em>DevOps</em> practices</li>
                        <li>Sharing my knowledge with others—both students and fellow developers</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 6. In a Nutshell -->
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border border-2 border-secondary">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>
                        <strong>In a nutshell</strong>: I’m an adaptable developer who merges
                        a strong <em>technical foundation</em> with a proven ability to
                        <em>communicate</em>, <em>mentor</em>, and <em>drive projects</em>
                        forward. With a passion for <em>innovation</em> and
                        <em>collaboration</em>, I’m looking to bring my expertise in
                        <strong>software development</strong>, <strong>cloud technologies</strong>,
                        and <strong>educational insight</strong> to organizations shaping
                        tomorrow’s tech landscape.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
